'''Courtney''' is the mother of a baby who had fetal surgery.

==History==
Courtney was pregnant. Her baby was delivered by [[Nicole Herman]] and [[Arizona Robbins]]. From there, she was given supplemental oxygen and taken to the NICU while they finished the c-section delivery and closed her incision.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
Courtney has a daughter. Given the fact that she was delivered by fetal surgeons, it's likely that she had some sort of condition which had been treated with surgery prior to her birth.
